# ==============================================================================
# Vercel AI Gateway Configuration
# ==============================================================================

# OPTION 1: Manual API Key (for local development without Vercel CLI)
# Get your key from: https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway
# AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# OPTION 2: OIDC Token (RECOMMENDED - automatic with Vercel CLI)
# Run: vercel link && vercel env pull
# This creates .env.vercel with VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN automatically
# No manual key needed - token is auto-refreshed

# ==============================================================================
# Setup Instructions
# ==============================================================================
# RECOMMENDED: Use OIDC Token (No manual key needed)
#   1. Install Vercel CLI: npm i -g vercel
#   2. Link project: vercel link
#   3. Pull environment: vercel env pull
#   4. Token is now available in .env.vercel (auto-refreshed)
#
# ALTERNATIVE: Use Manual API Key
#   1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
#   2. Get key from: https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway
#   3. Add to .env.local: AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=your_key
#
# ⚠️  NEVER commit .env.local or .env.vercel to git!
# ==============================================================================